title: United Kingdom Imports of Nickel & Related Articles
description: Imports of Nickel & Related Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 115.65 GBP Million in September from 126.28 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Nickel & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 71.75 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 172.16 GBP Million in May of 2007 and a record low of 19.47 GBP Million in August of 2003. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Nickel & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
